<h3>The love Definition</h3> 
Love is patient, <br><br>

Even though we can be complacent. <br><br>

Love never fails, nor does it fade,<br><br>

it is always there, even when you're afraid.<br><br>

Love endures all things without weakening,<br><br>

even when we can be very self-seeking.<br><br>

Love is neither jealous nor rudefull,<br><br>

instead, it is kind and thoughtful.<br><br>

So if you are ever in a bind,<br><br>

God's warm love is what you will always find.
